<number box="[668,723,1503,1527]" pageId="3" pageNumber="292" value="9.0" valueMax="11.0" valueMin="7.0">7–11</number>
forming a distinct club, segments 
<number box="[1112,1168,1503,1527]" pageId="3" pageNumber="292" value="9.5" valueMax="10.0" valueMin="9.0">9–10</number>
